---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/globals.css";
import { Header } from "../../components/Header";
import InnerPageCTA from "../../components/InnerPageCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="Lanzarote '22: parcelLab Company Offsite - parcelLab"
  description="A look back at parcelLab's 2022 company offsite in Lanzarote, where the team came together to connect, collaborate, and celebrate."
>
  <Header client:load />
  <main>
    <!-- Article Header -->
    <section class="section-generous">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
          <a href={`${b}/blog/`} class="group mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[#3D3AD3]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-0.5"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
            Back to blog
          </a>
          <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-[#3D3AD3]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Company Culture</span>
          <h1 class="text-display text-[var(--ink)]">Lanzarote '22: parcelLab Company Offsite</h1>
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">
            <span>By <strong class="font-medium text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">parcelLab Team</strong></span>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <time datetime="2022-08-15">August 15, 2022</time>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <span>4 min read</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Article Body -->
    <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-lg">
          At parcelLab, we believe that strong teams build strong products. That's why we make it a priority to bring our global team together regularly -- and this year, we headed to the beautiful island of Lanzarote for our company offsite.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Why Offsites Matter</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          With team members spread across offices in Munich, Boston, London, and Paris, our offsites are a chance to break down the barriers of remote and hybrid work. Meeting face-to-face builds the trust and camaraderie that make cross-functional collaboration so much more effective when we're back at our desks.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">A Week of Connection and Collaboration</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          The Lanzarote offsite combined strategic planning sessions with team-building activities and plenty of time to simply connect as people. Highlights included:
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 space-y-6">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--ink)]">Strategy Sessions</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
              Cross-functional workshops where teams from product, engineering, sales, and customer success aligned on our roadmap and shared insights from their respective markets. These sessions helped everyone understand the bigger picture and their role in it.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--ink)]">Team Activities</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
              From exploring the volcanic landscapes of Lanzarote to group dinners and beach outings, the team had plenty of opportunities to bond outside of work. These shared experiences create lasting memories and stronger working relationships.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--ink)]">Celebrating Wins</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
              We took time to recognize the achievements of the past year -- from major product launches to key customer partnerships. Celebrating together reinforces the impact of everyone's contributions.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Looking Ahead</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          The offsite left the team energized and aligned on the work ahead. With new product innovations in the pipeline, expanded market presence, and an ever-growing customer base, the second half of 2022 promises to be an exciting chapter for parcelLab.
        </p>

        <div class="my-12 border-t border-[var(--line)]"></div>

        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          Interested in joining a team that values connection, collaboration, and great customer experiences? Check out our careers page to see open positions across all our offices.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <InnerPageCTA />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
